page.title: 11MY DAY PART 2
page.content: Then at 10.50 it is the end of break time and I go back in class to do some work until dinner time at 12.00. I go home for lunch and play for a little while before going back to school at 1.10 p.m.For my lunch I have things like beans on toast,salad, luncheon meat and bread. I finish school at 3.00 and go home.I play outside until 5.30 when I have my dinner.After dinner I go outside again until it is dark then I come in and watch television.My favourite programmes are Grange Hill,Children's ITV and films. I go to bed between 9.00 and 9.30 p.m.
